    "body": "This is done (https://github.com/Giulio2002/snapshot-archive), but unfortunately, it turned out to be impractical\r\n\r\nit is able to read about 100k items every 12 minutes\r\n\r\nand we have currently around 260m items in the contract storage and 78m items in the accounts\r\n\r\nwhich means that the snapshot would take around 28 days to generate\r\n\r\nand the database is already 3.5 Tb, so I cannot put it on NVMe to speed it up",
